document.title: Brieven als Buit
document.intro: Web interface to a database of transcribed 17th to 19th centuary letters CLARIN based login required. The Clarin federation accepts login from many european institutions. please see http://www.clarin.eu/content/service-provider-federation for more details Fragments from the texts are presented according to the configuration that is selected by the user.
